    <p>Need to Ensure Information Security:</p>
    <p>Confidentiality</p>
    <p>Integrity</p>
    <p>Availability</p>
    <p>Challenges of Ensuring Information Security</p>
    <p>Large spectrum of possible points of attack</p>
    <p>Requires specialised, up-to-date knowledge</p>
    <p>Users need to deal with/trust in diverse approaches</p>
    <p>Neglect of security issues until something goes wrong might be</p>
    <p>appealing</p>
    <p>Can common, certified, and widely-used security functionality</p>
    <p>serve as foundation for secure provision of patient-centered</p>
    <p>services?</p>
